description: Artist: Vida V. | This is an early design for the icon of TwoToJazz app for iPad, drawn in TwoToJazz itself. TwoToJazz is a multi-touch iPad creativity app developed by Vida that was offered in the App Store from late 2013 to late 2018. She has further developed TwoToJazz, and continues using it as her own unique digital artistic tool | Creation date: April 4, 2013
